text: Sicko was a 2007 documentary movie made by Michael Moore. It explores the American health care system, and compares it to the United Kingdom's, Canada's, France's and Cuba's. It made $24.5 million, making it the third- highest grossing documentary of all time. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:2007 documentary movies Category:American documentary movies Category:American independent movies
